Package com.topcoder.search.builder

Interface Summary
ConnectionInformation Deprecated. This public class is not used any more
SearchFragmentBuilder This is the interface that is used to define the contract for building a SearchContext out of a provided filter.
SearchStrategy The search strategy is responsible for connecting to the datastore, building the necessary query String (if applicable) and executing it against the datastore.
SearchStringBuilder Deprecated. This public class is not used any more
 

Class Summary
ConnectionStrategy Deprecated. This public class is not used any more
SearchBuilderHelper This helper class of this component.
SearchBundle This class represents a search bundle.
SearchBundleManager This class manages a collection of SearchBundle objects.
SearchContext This is a State object that is used to hold the current status of building a Search.
ValidationResult This class models the filter validtion result.
 

Exception Summary
DuplicatedElementsException The items insert into the DataSource should not exist before.
OperationNotSupportedException It is thrown if the intended operation is not supported.
PersistenceOperationException It is thrown if connection to data store fails, or any operations over data store fails.
SearchBuilderConfigurationException It is thrown if any error occurs when reading the configuration file,for construct the manager via the namespace from the configration file.
SearchBuilderException This is a custom exception.
UnrecognizedFilterException This exception is thrown if a SearchStrategy or SearchFragmentBuilder is unable to recognize the provided filter.
